"9", "10", "11" up to "23" implies the respective JDK levels 9, 10, 11 up to 23 and api levels AST.JLS9, AST.JLS10, AST.JLS11 up to AST.JLS23. Additional legal values may be added later. "org.eclipse.jdt.core.compiler.problem.enablePreviewFeatures" - indicates whether the preview is enabled or disabled legal values are "enabled" and "disabled" implying preview enabled and disabled respectively.
